HEADWORD: Star stereogram
<hw>Star stereogram</hw>. <def>A view of the universe of brighter stars
as it would appear to an observer transported into space outside or
beyond our universe of stars.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

